README.md

Awesome

     A curated list of awesome resources for building
     [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smart_TV]Smart TV apps

   [https://github.com/vitalets/awesome-smart-tv][27913047-7c3a5e60-6267-1
   1e7-8bd1-bef2bf3cd753.png]

   [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smart_TV]Smart TV is a growing platform
   of TVs having access to internet and allowing to serf web-sites and
   install applications. It has own ecosystem with main players like
   Samsung, LG, Android TV and Apple TV. In this list you will find
   official and third-party resources for developing Smart TV apps and
   communicating with TV from remote devices.

